    <item>
      <title>亚洲在油价和美元之间陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/business/iran-war-dollar-rupee-won.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从印度到东南亚再到韩国，随着各国政府竞相争夺以美元计价的燃料，货币正在崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/business/iran-war-dollar-rupee-won.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 23:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党要求 ICE 限制，国土安全谈判陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/homeland-security-shutdown-republicans-congress.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在共和党提出从国土安全部拨款法案中删除用于 ICE 执法的资金的第二天，民主党坚称该协议必须包括对联邦特工的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/politics/homeland-security-shutdown-republicans-congress.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 23:25:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么休斯顿布什机场的延误情况比其他机场更严重？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/tsa-airport-delays-houston-bush.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，美国运输安全管理局 (T.S.A.) 期间，全国机场排起了长队。人员短缺，但布什洲际机场的乘客却等待了四个多小时才能通过检查站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/25/us/tsa-airport-delays-houston-bush.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 22:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
